<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
        .header { background-color: #1a1a1a; padding: 30px 20px; text-align: center; }
        .header h1 { color: #ffffff; margin: 0; font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .content { padding: 40px 30px; color: #4a4a4a; line-height: 1.6; }
        .content h2 { color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 22px; margin-top: 0; }
        .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 14px 28px; background-color: #D19D94; color: #ffffff !important; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 20px; }
        .footer { background-color: #f1f1f1; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #888888; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Naisha Creations</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <!-- Handlebars uses double curly braces for dynamic data -->
            <h2>Welcome to the family, {{firstName}}! ✨</h2>
            <p>We are absolutely thrilled to have you here. At Naisha Creations, we craft premium, hand-poured candles designed to bring warmth, peace, and beautiful scents into your space.</p>
            <p>Your account has been successfully created. You can now track your orders, save your favorite addresses, and even customize your own bespoke candles.</p>
            
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{frontendUrl}}/collections" class="btn">Shop Our Collection</a>
            </div>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Warmly,<br>The Naisha Creations Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            &copy; {{year}} Naisha Creations. All rights reserved.<br>
            If you have any questions, simply reply to this email.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>